                        geometric motifs.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2">
                        <locus target="#16r">Fol. 16r: </locus>
                        <desc>Cross and birds.</desc>Coloured (red, black) talismanic
                        drawing.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3">
                        <locus target="#17v">Fol. 17v: </locus>
                        <desc>Geometric motifs.</desc>Coloured (red, black) talismanic
                        drawing.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4">
                        <locus target="#38v">Fol. 38v: </locus>
                        <desc>Angel.</desc>Coloured (red, black) talismanic drawing of angel
